    "All these simulations and datasets offer new opportunities for expanding our knowledge of the Earth system.",
    "By training ML models on historical solar data and corresponding climate records, these algorithms have the potential to improve our understanding of solar forcing and its relationship with Earth's climate, contributing to more accurate climate predictions and extracting new non-linear relations and patterns [172].",
